<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171208>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Longitarsus bethae sp. n. habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171208/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171209>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 4. Longitarsus bethae sp. n. 2, 3) Head in frontal view. Supraanntennal callus, AC. Transversal sulcus, TS. Mid frontal sulcus, MFS. Ocular sulcus, OS. Orbital sulcus, ORS. Supraorbital sulcus, SOS. Supra frontal vertical sulcus, SFVS. Supraorbital puncture, SP. Frontoclypeal longitudinal ridge, FCLR. 4). Head in lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171209/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171210>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5 – 8. Longitarsus bethae sp. n. Mouthparts: 5) Mandibular mola. 6) Labrum 7) Labium. 8) Maxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171210/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171211>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 11. Longitarsus bethae sp. n 10) Meso and metasternun. 11) Longitarsus bethae sp. n. Elytron." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171211/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171212>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13 – 16. Aedeagus: 13 – 14) Ventral views. 15) Lateral view. 16) Dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171213>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 18. 17) Vaginal palpi. Figure 18) Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171213/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

